Add right-aligned "RudderStack tab" status bar entry (PRO-5528)

Match the Figma "IDE Footer" (node 101-3202) by introducing a small
workbench contribution that registers a static, non-clickable status
bar entry on the right edge, just left of the notifications bell.

The contribution lives under a new code-server-owned folder
`contrib/codeServerProfiles/browser/` so we don't have to touch any
existing stock contribution. It registers at `WorkbenchPhase.Restored`
(after the layout and other status bar entries have settled) and uses
a priority value picked to sit immediately to the left of the bell
(which uses `Number.NEGATIVE_INFINITY`).

The visible copy is a placeholder; the design team has not yet locked
the final string. See the inline TODO comment in the contribution file.

